# âœ”ï¸ **2. Jest for Frontend (React/Next.js)**

ğŸ“Œ Folder: `frontend/`
ğŸ“Œ Purpose:

* Test React components (`Post.tsx`, `EnhancedFilter`, `NewsForm`, etc.)
* Test UI state
